        <h3 class="section_title size_22"> ORDER TERMS </h3> 
       </div> 
       <div class="flex_item right_col"> 
        <div class="content_text"> 
         <ul>
          <li>Delivery fees will be charged on all McDelivery® orders and each other may be subject to minimum order limit. Please refer to the mobile app or telephone ordering for details.</li>
          <br> 
          <li>The payment choices are either cash or debit/credit card (VISA/MasterCard/JCB) for orders via mobile app.</li>
          <br> 
          <ul>
           <li>Where payment is made by debit/credit card (VISA/MasterCard/JCB), you acknowledge agree and consent that your personal data such as your name and debit/credit card number may be collected by third parties (located within and outside of Hong Kong) processing such debit/credit card transactions, including debit/credit card companies, banks and payment gateways, and, subject to their respective personal data privacy policies and applicable laws, may be used, processed and stored by such third parties to facilitate payments that you now or subsequently make for orders placed.</li>
           <br> 
           <li>For the Privacy Policy for Payment Gateway Services (VISA/MasterCard/JCB), please refer to<a href="www.mastercard.com/gateway/privacy/privacy.html">www.mastercard.com/gateway/privacy/privacy.html</a></li>
          </ul>
          <br> 
          <li>For McDelivery® telephone orders, only cash payment is allowed when you order from telephone ordering service.。</li>
          <br> 
          <li>Cash payment shall be made at point of delivery of food. Cash payment shall be made in Hong Kong dollars only and do not accept HK$1,000 banknote at the time of delivery.</li>
          <br> 
          <li>Delivery service is only available in selected areas of Hong Kong. Please call our McDelivery® hotline at 2338 2338 for details.</li>
          <br> 
          <ul>
           <li>Delivery service by McDelivery® may be delayed in the event of bad weather, traffic and/or uncontrollable conditions. Delivery service will be suspended during black rainstorm warning, or the hoisting of typhoon signal no. 8 or above.</li>
          </ul>
          <br> 
          <li>Product information pricing and images available at mobile app or telephone ordering service are for reference only. Availability of products may vary at individual restaurants. Prices and products listed herein are subject to change by McDonald's from time to time without prior notice. Customers should refer to prices and products quoted at the time of order.</li>
          <br> 
          <li>Mobile app ordering or telephone ordering cannot be made in conjunction with other discounts, special or promotional offer unless otherwise specified. Food Coupons and Gift Certificates of McDonald's® and McCafé® will not be accepted unless otherwise specified.</li>
          <br> 
          <li>Different food and beverage items are available at different times. Breakfast menu orders made via mobile app or telephone ordering service are taken from 3:45am until 10:45am and regular menu orders are taken from 10:45am until 3:45am via mobile app or telephone ordering.</li>
          <br> 
          <li>McDelivery® service is available for the food and beverage items listed in the mobile app McDelivery® service is only available for selected McCafé® drinks.</li>
          <br> 
          <li>McDelivery® service is not available for Create Your Taste™ food.</li>
          <br> 
          <li>For any purchase of Happy Meal(s)® and/or Happy Meal toy(s), McDonald's reserves the right to select the type of toy(s) to be delivered.</li>
          <br> 
          <li>For any Chicken McNuggets® purchase, Chicken McNuggets® sauce will be provided free of charge - one free sauce unit for the purchase of 4 pcs. or 6 pcs. of Chicken McNuggets®, two free sauce units for the purchase of 9 pcs, and four free sauce units for the purchase of 18 pcs. For the purchase of other non-Chicken McNuggets® related food and/or a request of additional Chicken McNuggets® sauce unit, HK$1.5 will be charged each sauce unit.</li>
          <br> 
          <li>For any Hotcakes purchase, 2 packs of margarine will be provided free of charge.</li>
          <br> 
          <li>Burger Lovers Combo and themed sharing combo are only available for mobile app ordering or telephone ordering with no dine-in.</li>
          <br> 
          <ul>
           <li>Enjoy an extra treat with standard price food order of each All-new Meal Combo or Sharing Combo by mobile app or Telephone Ordering orders.</li>
          </ul>
