       <div class="flex_item right_col"> 
        <div class="content_text">
          McDonald's Privacy Policy will apply to any personal information, including but not limited to, first and last names, phone numbers, addresses and email addresses, which are voluntarily submitted by you when using this website and when ordering from us through the mobile app or telephone ordering service. Such personal information collected from you will be used for processing and following up your orders and payments and for other directly related purposes. You may view and/or correct your personal information by updating "My Personal Information" in your account.
         <br> 
         <br> We would also like to send you direct marketing communications with respect to offers or promotions in relation to McDonald's food and beverages and related products, catering and delivery services and events, games and activities ("Marketing Materials") but we cannot do so unless you indicate your consent to receive Marketing Materials from McDonald's by checking the relevant tick box when you register for use of our mobile app or telephone ordering service.
         <br> 
         <br> You will also receive oral notification of our intention to send you Marketing Materials when placing your order through our McDelivery® telephone ordering service. Your consent to such use of your personal information will be sought by our telephone operator at the time of your order and subsequently confirmed by us in writing within 14 days of your telephone order.
         <br> 
         <br> If at any time you decide you no longer wish to receive direct marketing communications from us, you may withdraw your consent by updating "My Personal Information" in your account or indicating your opt-out to our telephone operator when you place an order with our telephone ordering service.
         <br> 
         <br> Please refer to our Privacy Policy (which forms part of these Terms and Conditions) to see how we collect, use or disclose personal information that we may collect from you. Please check our official website (<a href="www.mcdonalds.com.hk">www.mcdonalds.com.hk</a>) for the most up-to-date version of our Privacy Policy.
         <br> 
        </div> 
       </div> 
      </div> 
